{"tid":2129641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"吉林公安廳副廳長出版著作《平安經》 內容全部為平安平安 官媒都揶揄","createTime":"2020-07-28T17:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T01:51:14.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb735404e0e4770088867c5126380c5bcf54241","tid":2129641,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:33:53.000Z","msg":"「西安火車站北站平安、鄭州火車站東站平安、上海虹橋火車站平安⋯⋯」吉林省公安廳黨委副書記、常務副廳長賀電創作的《平安經》，整本書以「XXX平安」造句，引發內地網民討論。就連《人民日報》旗下公眾號「俠客島」作者都揶揄，指換着是他，「即日能創作10萬字」，「有沒有出版社願意出版？」有內媒周二（28日）向吉林省公安廳職員查詢，對方回應創作《平安經》是賀電工餘時間的行為，加上工作繁忙，賀電暫不方便接受採訪。<br />\n<br />\n《平安經》突然受到關注，是因為有網民周一（27日）晚在微博上載《平安經》的封面照片及書中內容，可見作者為賀電；部份頁面內容顯示，書本以「XXX平安」為主題，例如該書第十篇「人類眾生平安」之「眾生身心平安」章節分為「身心平安、感覺平安、呼吸系統平安、消化系統平安、神經系統平安」；「身心平安」寫道，「眼平安、耳平安、鼻平安、舌平安、身平安、意平安」；「性別平安」分為「男性平安、女性平安」；「各年齡平安」分為「初生平安、滿月平安、百天平安、1歲平安、2歲平安、3歲平安&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n吉林省應急管理廳微信公號在4月9日曾轉發《平安經》，書評是「值得一讀」。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sYZx1yytqYJ9N_DtOqqQyDl43KM=/802x1294/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5BPHZ77E4HNHP6TLI5LUXS34JM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsYZx1yytqYJ9N_DtOqqQyDl43KM%3D%2F802x1294%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5BPHZ77E4HNHP6TLI5LUXS34JM.png&h=fdf85233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bgnSaltRDC35npjMaIBv6dTHoJY=/802x1065/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UDOFY6FURERTYJAF63FRZFIAMY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbgnSaltRDC35npjMaIBv6dTHoJY%3D%2F802x1065%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUDOFY6FURERTYJAF63FRZFIAMY.png&h=eb0578d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澎湃新聞網／《人民日報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200728/TXZNT2B5LRT4MQR4OU4VRBBFNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200728%2FTXZNT2B5LRT4MQR4OU4VRBBFNI%2F&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD2a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=6cb36ed5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200728%2FTXZNT2B5LRT4MQR4OU4VRBBFNI%2F&h=2f8e543d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200728/TXZNT2B5LRT4MQR4OU4VRBBFNI/</a>"},{"pid":"e617296c4799ab7f5986b06a29565b6b34803a45","tid":2129641,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:34:49.000Z","msg":"我火屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be07bf3b15a6550edc54fd379fa840ec89e0c98","tid":2129641,"uid":61882,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:38:01.000Z","msg":"吉林省發來<ins>賀電</ins>"},{"pid":"7a8d35062c291c00d5ffa55e2c4d554709a1c950","tid":2129641,"uid":164579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:46:33.000Z","msg":"64歲平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0db78006b0a85630c9c1f4e4cfdd1ce31dff39","tid":2129641,"uid":13151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T20:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17c214e6d60abf19ffd9827191ecabb0a8f49b8","tid":2129641,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T22:55:26.000Z","msg":"香港港平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615463f4c40e1becccae8f234694baafe4353bae","tid":2129641,"uid":188282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T22:57:32.000Z","ms